-Sáu.

1085
00:58:27,400 --> 00:58:28,350
-Hay Kir?
-Năm.

1086
00:58:28,350 --> 00:58:29,440
Bốn...

1087
00:58:29,440 --> 00:58:30,150
Ba...

1088
00:58:30,150 --> 00:58:30,650
Hai...

1089
00:58:30,650 --> 00:58:32,480
-Mày sẽ đi đầu.
-Một.

1090
00:58:32,650 --> 00:58:33,530
Zero!

1091
00:58:33,530 --> 00:58:34,780
Bourbon!

1092
00:58:51,750 --> 00:58:54,050
